Added `network_driver` database field to the `Platform` model.
Added `ansible_driver`, `hier_config_driver`, `netmiko_driver`, `ntc_templates_driver`, `pyats_driver`, `pyntc_driver`, and `scrapli_driver` derived attributes on the `Platform` model.
Added `CONSTANCE_DATABASE_CACHE_BACKEND = 'default'` to `settings.py`, which should improve performance a bit.
Added support for `NETWORK_DRIVERS` config setting.
